mkdir node-todo-api

cd node-todo-api 

npm init
(Press Enter for all the questions)

Create a new folder "playground" for testing or learning purpose. This folder is not the part of todo app.

touch playground/mongodb-connect.js

First, we need to install the library

Command to install the library

npm install mongodb@2.2.5 --save